snippet.title: The Tallest Man on Earth - Live from the Finger Lakes featuring Courtney Marie Andrews
snippet.description:
This week my friend Courtney Marie Andrews is going to stop by the livestream! We’ll talk about the tour we were supposed to be starting this week, and maybe I can get her to play a song. I will play covers from your requests and among others a TTMOE song that references three older TTMOE songs in the outro. Guess what the hell I’m talking about. See you here this Friday, May 8th at 3pm eastern time (21:00 CET).

snippet.title: The Tallest Man on Earth - Live from The Finger Lakes #StayHome #WithMe
snippet.description:
For this week’s livestream we’re just going to hang out and play some songs.  I have hundreds of questions that I haven’t been able to answer yet and thousands of requests for covers. Thank you for this lovely ocean to swim in. Keep them coming at questionsforkristian@gmail.com. I’ll look after the plants and probably talk to Fran. See you here this Friday, May 1st at 3pm eastern time (21:00 CET)!

snippet.title: The Tallest Man on Earth - I Will Play "Weather Of A Killing Kind" #StayHome #WithMe
snippet.description:
Email to request covers for next week's stream: questionsforkristian@gmail.com

I’m going to do another livestream / hang from my room this Friday, April 17th at 3pm eastern time (21:00 CET). I’m still learning how to do these, I will try to tame the buffering monster the days leading up to it. I will get super fast vision so I can read your questions in the comments. No, I probably can’t do that. So.  If you have a question you’d like me to answer, email it to this address and I’ll try. Email: questionsforkristian@gmail.com
